General.Name: GasLog Partners LP
General.Description: GasLog Partners LP acquires, owns, and operates liquefied natural gas (LNG) carriers provides LNG transportation services worldwide. As of February 28, 2023, it operated a fleet of 14 LNG carriers. The company was founded in 2014 and is based in Piraeus, Greece. As of July 13, 2023, GasLog Partners LP operates as a subsidiary of GasLog Ltd.
